    {
      "chinese": "《原創保護條例》的全銜是《原住民族傳統智慧創作保護條例》，簡稱原創保護條例，本課文沿用該簡稱。原創保護條例是依據中華民國憲法的增修條文而制定的。首先，立法院於2005年通過《原住民基本法》，終於在2007年12月制定了《原住民族傳統智慧創作保護條例》，並由「原住民族委員會」為其主管機關。",
      "ab": "Ngayan na bale “Yencwang Pawhu Tiyawri” nii we, “Yencumincu Cwantong Cuhwe Cwangco Pawhu Tiyawri”, asi daha kesi “Yencwang Pawhu Tiyawri”. So kiya ka patis nii duri. Pusu pnyahan na kesun\r\n “Yencwang Pawhu Tiyawri” nii we, pnrbangan smmalu Senhwa nConghwaminkwo nii. Plaale han we, knkawas 2005 ciida, wada spooda na Rihwayen ka “Yencuming Cipunhwa”, kika knkawas 2007 idas 12 de, qulung daha bale wada slmeyun ka “Yencumincu Cwantong Cuhwe Cwangco Pawhu Tiyawri” ma, sbege na “Yencumincu Weyenhwe” ka pqlahang “Yencwang Pawhu Tiyawri” nii.",
